OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCladding: More flat owners 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fto be freed from bills     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Flat owners will not have to pay to    
OL,6, remove dangerous cladding from         
OL,7, lower-height buildings under new       
OL,8, government plans, BBC Newsnight        
OL,9, understands.                           
OL,11,FIt means leaseholders in buildings of  
OL,12,Fbetween 11 and 18.5m will no longer be 
OL,13,Fexpected to take out personal loans to 
OL,14,Fcover the cost of the work.            
OL,16,FInstead, the government will try to    
OL,17,Fsecure up to #4bn from developers      
OL,18,Ftowards the costs.                     
OL,20,FIt had already promised to pay to      
OL,21,Fremove cladding in taller buildings.   
